description: TO AGREE TO THE REPORT OF THE CONFERENCE COMMITTEE REGARDING AMENDMENTS TO H. R. 1033 (36 STAT. L. 1, APP. 7/2/1909), A BILL PROVIDING FOR THE THIRTEENTH AND SUBSEQUENT DECENNIAL CENSUSES.  (P.1410-2)
